      <title>Trump sets new tariff rates and deadlines. And, rabbis speak out on starvation in Gaza</title>
      <author>Suzanne Nuyen</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/08/01/g-s1-80579/up-first-newsletter-trump-tariffs-gaza-starvation-israel</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2025/08/01/g-s1-80579/up-first-newsletter-trump-tariffs-gaza-starvation-israel</comments>
