      <title>GOP divided over Epstein files. And, Columbia disciplines student protesters</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/07/23/g-s1-78877/up-first-newsletter-jeffrey-epstein-obama-administration-russia-columbia-university-student-protestors</link>
